7120,IssuesEvent,2015-06-04 17:57:07+00:00,33146014,Yelp/bravado-core,1528697,prat0318,49071,Yelp,closed,Inline schema failed to validate,[],[],3,"I'm not sure if this is expected or not, I tried to create a response with an inline schema, something like this:

```json
    {                                                                                                                                                                              
        ""swagger"": ""2.0"",                                                                                                                                                                      
        ""info"": {                                                                                                                                                                              
            ""version"": ""1.0.0"",                                                                                                                                                                
