7627,IssuesEvent,2016-09-14 00:10:59+00:00,19746601,litl/backoff,1070323,duckpunch,190361,litl,opened,Default handlers log too much and there's no way to disable them through the library API,[],[],0,"I'm trying to use `backoff` with a login function that connects to an external server.  The code looks something like this.

