9399,IssuesEvent,2016-05-26 14:47:51+00:00,57309106,inveniosoftware/invenio-records-files,189798,jirikuncar,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,api: `flush` should fetch data from bucket,[],[],0,"### Problem

Deposit `_files` are not sync when using files REST API directly.

### Proposal

Use `self.dumps()` in `flush` method (see https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio-records-files/blob/master/invenio_records_files/api.py#L143)

```diff
diff --git a/invenio_records_files/api.py b/invenio_records_files/api.py
index 8ba70c2..f6ddf7e 100644
--- a/invenio_records_files/api.py
+++ b/invenio_records_files/api.py
