11639,IssuesEvent,2016-11-21 19:24:29+00:00,70530854,awslabs/serverless-application-model,22755571,sanathkr,3299148,awslabs,closed,SNS topic to being linked to Function?,"[{'id': 458889979, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/awslabs/serverless-application-model/labels/question', 'name': 'question', 'color': 'cc317c', 'default': True}]",[],1,"Can I use `!Ref` to reference an SNS topic defined in the same template? The following pseudo-code is basically what I'm trying to achieve. The function and topic gets created but the function does not have a trigger for the SNS topic automatically created.

