11744,IssuesEvent,2017-11-08 18:48:57+00:00,21954559,datamade/usaddress,26750536,tipevo-staub,3723931,datamade,opened,usaddress.tag error when directional appears in the town,[],[],0,"Looks like something goes back to parsing Street info from Place/State info when a directional word (East) appears in the city/town place.

