Got this:
ERROR: Unable to tag this string because more than one area of the string has the same label

ORIGINAL STRING:  745 Forbes St East Hartford CT
PARSED TOKENS:    [(u'745', 'AddressNumber'), (u'Forbes', 'StreetName'), (u'St', 'StreetNamePostType'), (u'East', 'StreetNamePreDirectional'), (u'Hartford', 'StreetName'), (u'CT', 'StreetNamePostType')]
