gin': 'laurenlichtman', 'id': 25990164, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/25990164?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/laurenlichtman', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/laurenlichtman/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}, {'login': 'navakk9', 'id': 26124065, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/26124065?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/navakk9', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/navakk9/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"## Summary

A long-needed change. Thanks to @laurenlichtman for bringing it up.

**Current order of the content recommendation subsections:**

1. Most popular
2. Next steps
3. Resume
4. Overview (to be renamed)

**Proposed reordering:**

1. Resume
2. Next steps
3. Most popular
4. Overview (to be renamed)

**Justification:**
Presenting ""Resume"" followed by ""Next steps"" is more in line with supporting a personalized learning experience. The Learner would see content that is most related to what they were most recently engaging with first, without needing to scroll or click through a labyrinth of topics.

Please write comments providing further justifications for either ordering, as there is not consensus in the team for the proposed reordering.

## System information

*Please specify the Kolibri version you were using and your operating system!*

 - Version: Kolibri 0.5.0beta1.dev33
 - Operating system: MacOS Sierra
 - Browser: Chrome
",{},{}
