12509,IssuesEvent,2017-09-07 13:46:11+00:00,30863890,frictionlessdata/tableschema-py,557395,roll,5912125,frictionlessdata,closed,License issue: 'rfc3987' is GPL,"[{'id': 177576893, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/frictionlessdata/tableschema-py/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'fc2929', 'default': True}, {'id': 683203926, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/frictionlessdata/tableschema-py/labels/%7Bcurrent%7D', 'name': '{current}', 'color': 'ffffff', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'roll', 'id': 557395, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/557395?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/roll', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/roll/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",1,"Hi,

The Tableschema library lists as part of its requirements the library `rfc3987>=1.3,<2.0`. The library [rfc3987](https://github.com/dgerber/rfc3987) is GPL licensed. And it seems not to be used anywhere in the source code (according to a quick grep check).

The library [rfc3986](http://rfc3986.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) is used, but that is Apache licensed and is less restrictive.

Can `rfc3987` be removed from the dependencies?",{},{}
