Logged from file exceptions.py, line 770
$ echo $ZSH_VERSION 
5.3.1
```


## Expected Behavior
<!-- What do you think should happen? -->
The source script should work as it did with `conda<=4.3*`. My current workaround is to prepend `~/anaconda/bin` to `$PATH` manually.

