14048,IssuesEvent,2018-06-20 23:15:30+00:00,24375248,blockstack/blockstack-core,459947,jcnelson,8165984,blockstack,closed,Ways to decrease name costs,"[{'id': 807888335, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw4MDc4ODgzMzU=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/blockstack/blockstack-core/labels/area/protocol', 'name': 'area/protocol', 'color': '1d76db', 'default': False}, {'id': 807888174, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw4MDc4ODgxNzQ=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/blockstack/blockstack-core/labels/kind/discussion', 'name': 'kind/discussion', 'color': 'fbca04', 'default': False}]",[],9,"This is a list of ways we can decrease name cost both in terms of bitcoin and time:

1. don't spend dust utxos (see #453)
2. remove `NAME_TRANSFER` step (require portal provide the owner_address private key)
3. remove multisig from core
4. pass browser bitcoin wallet private key
5. `NAME_TRANSFER` & `NAME_REGISTER` should take a value hash (removing need for `NAME_UPDATE` when performing these transactions.)


tagging @jcnelson @kantai @muneeb-ali @shea256 ",{},{}
