14269,IssuesEvent,2017-09-08 12:02:04+00:00,23953531,androguard/androguard,248875,Rafiot,8758456,androguard,closed,Crash when decompiling (file attached),"[{'id': 128903814, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/androguard/androguard/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'fc2929', 'default': True}, {'id': 626414155, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/androguard/androguard/labels/decompiler', 'name': 'decompiler', 'color': 'c5def5', 'default': False}]",[],10,"Probable regression found during the tests with viper: https://travis-ci.org/viper-framework/viper/jobs/251812309#L1195 (I re-ran the tests after removing the cache and using the HEAD of androguard)

