14336,IssuesEvent,2017-04-12 14:44:03+00:00,45062555,F5Networks/f5-common-python,18006037,wojtek0806,8935905,F5Networks,closed,LTM pool Monitor property,[],"[{'login': 'wojtek0806', 'id': 18006037, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/18006037?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/wojtek0806', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/wojtek0806/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",1,"There is an issue that affects all known versions with monitor property, specifically x of m:
````
 min 1 of { /Common/https_443 /Common/icmp }

````

REST has problems processing {} that are in that string, the workaround now is to submit this property string without {}. 
````
