14540,IssuesEvent,2016-02-11 17:46:04+00:00,26516210,letsencrypt/letsencrypt,1750103,schoen,9289019,letsencrypt,closed,Problem getting cert: CSR generated automatically without SAN,[],[],2,"I would like to request a certificate using a CSR for which I have minimal control over the generation. This CSR is generated without Subject Alternative Name and there is no way to force it. I don't have access to the private key to create a CSR myself either.

