15624,IssuesEvent,2016-07-18 22:49:22+00:00,37496521,nteract/nteract,836375,rgbkrk,12401040,nteract,opened,Monorepo,[],[],0,"In order to approach having more components available for an online version of the nteract components (you know, in your friendly browser instead of Electron) we need to either

* Separate more of our components into separate repositories (including actions, reducers, etc.)

or

* create a [monorepo](https://github.com/babel/babel/blob/master/doc/design/monorepo.md)

I'm in favor of exporting components _directly_ from nteract/nteract to assist with this so that's it's easy to work on the desktop app as a standalone in tandem with these core components. Especially since the API keeps evolving for actions, reducers, etc.",{},{}
