16535,IssuesEvent,2018-03-13 22:55:28+00:00,91379993,tensorflow/tensorboard,710113,nfelt,15658638,tensorflow,closed,tensorboard could not found event files if path has Chinese charactors under Windows.,"[{'id': 628269506, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/tensorflow/tensorboard/labels/(%E2%95%AF%C2%B0%E2%96%A1%C2%B0)%E2%95%AFwindows', 'name': '(╯°□°)╯windows', 'color': 'd93f0b', 'default': False}]",[],3,"Dear team,

On my machine, tensorboard inspect works, but no graph shown in web(it says no event files found) under Windows.

