  log2\train

  These tags are in log2\test:
  audio - 
  histograms

**If I copy the log2 directory to D:\PythonProjects\log**
run D:\PythonProjects>tensorboard --logdir=log, everyting is OK.

To trace the source code:
I found:
for inspect command, it enumerates the directory with the raw logdir argument(e.g. log)
for web, in testboard/backend/application.py
    def parse_event_files_spec
         ...
         if uri_pattern.match(path) is None:
             path = os.path.realpath(path)        # path convert to full path
    
after that, when enumerate the directory, is_directory(file_io.py) always return false.
If I comment the line of path convert, everything is OK.
Please take a look of is_directory(indee pywrap_tensorflow.IsDirectory).

Regards and Thanks!

Jumpapex.",{},{}
