17413,IssuesEvent,2018-06-01 09:06:11+00:00,50646767,raiden-network/raiden,1658405,LefterisJP,19666847,raiden-network,opened,Create Smart Contract Proxies that work with the new contracts,[],[],0,"Part of the integration of the new smart contracts into the Raiden core.

Create a second version of the smart contract proxies that keeps the same interface but works with the new contracts. Just provide a different name, e.g. `Registry2`. Once they are all done and integration is ready to happen we can remove the old proxies and rename the new ones.

The purpose of this issue is to parallelize work and avoid conflicts (as much as possible)",{},{}
