17429,IssuesEvent,2016-12-01 08:35:57+00:00,60605358,DataMedSci/pymchelper,7374733,grzanka,19749591,DataMedSci,opened,Position of the first bin in DDD generator,[],[],0,"Currently position of the first item in DDD files is the center of first Z bin in SH12A DDD scrorer.
Let us assume that SH12A DDD binning along Z spans from 0 to 50 cm with 1000 bins.
This gives bins of width 0.05 cm (0.5 mm). Center of the first bin is located at 0.025 cm (0.25mm) thus the first line of DDD would currently look like:

```
#   z[g/cm**2] dE/dz[MeV/(g/cm**2)] FWHM1[g/cm**2] factor FWHM2[g/cm**2]
!ddd
0.025 1.09572 0.0188768 0.99994 0.254359
```

DDD files found in TRiP98 distribution have data starting with Z = 0, i.e.

```
#   z[g/cm**2] dE/dz[MeV/(g/cm**2)] FWHM1[g/cm**2] factor FWHM2[g/cm**2]
!ddd
 0 107.973
 1.35437 106.478
```",{},{}
