    """"""
    class Meta:
        proxy = True
```

How can i restrict fields to subclass proxy models i.e I need only some fields from StudyPlanTemplateModel to create object for StaticStudyPlanTemplateModel other fields that not required for this class should be None but that fields may require while creating DynamicStudyPlanTemplateModel object",{},{}
